{"type":null,"faqId":43646,"title":"唤醒词训练时需要注意什么？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">唤醒词训练时，请在安静的环境下录音。这样可以减少其他人声或噪音带来的误操作。训练的时候</span><span class=\"s2\">建议45°左右握持手机，距离20至40cm，并尽量使用日常生活中最自然的语速、语调进行训练；千万不要对MIC进行训练和唤醒，会影响录音的质量和唤醒的成功率。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9147","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399204000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音唤醒,唤醒词,训练,注意","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}